# === carry_chain.4004 ===
# Demonstrate the 4004's carry-out semantics. IAC on 0xF wraps to 0 and
# sets CY = 1. The next instruction (CLC) shows how to drop the carry.
#
# After execution:
#   ACC = 0     (wrapped from 0xF + 1)
#   CY  = 0     (CLC cleared the carry-out)

DF   # LDM 15    ACC = 0xF (max 4-bit unsigned)
F2   # IAC       ACC = 0, CY = 1 (carry-out of bit 3)
F1   # CLC       CY = 0 (drop the carry; ACC unchanged)
